<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_b01e1b13c559.aspx"><b>周颂·载见</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonb01e1b13c559">
<p>载见辟王，曰求厥章。龙旂阳阳，和铃央央。鞗革有鸧，休有烈光。率见昭考，以孝以享。以介眉寿，永言保之，思皇多祜。烈文辟公，绥以多福，俾缉熙于纯嘏。</p>
